summary: The Backrooms are a creepy fictional place that started on the internet. It's like a huge, endless maze of empty rooms, existing outside of normal reality. People have made up stories about different levels and scary creatures there. A YouTuber named Kane Parsons made popular videos about the Backrooms, which got a lot of attention and inspired even more content. Now, Parsons is making a movie about it!
title: The Backrooms
